<td>
<center><b>Thomas Hariot (1560-1621)</b></center>

<ul>
  <li>pursued wide range of interests
    <ul>
      <li>mathematics </li>
      <li>astronomy </li>
      <li>alchemy </li>
      <li>optics (used telescope) </li>
      <li>languages </li>
      <li>voyages and exploration </li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>served as Ralegh's personal emissary on 1585-1586 voyage </li>
  <li>took astronomical observations at sea </li>
  <li>navigational consultant </li>
  <li>studied Indians </li>
  <li>supervised mapping of new territories </li>
  <li>noted natural phenomena </li>
  <li>surveyed economic resources of the region </li>
  <li>wrote <i><a href="week4j.html">Briefe
